    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait so if it's CIF, the seller is the one responsible for the insurance, but if the cargo gets lost or damaged somewhere in the middle of the ocean during transit, who actually files the claim? and what kind of \"unforeseen incidents\" are typically covered under those CIF clauses?",
